<template>
  <NewMessage/>
</template>

<script>

import NewMessage from "@/components/NewMessage"

async function getPokemonData(query) {

  let url = `https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?limit=${query}&offset=0`
  let response = await fetch(url)
  let pokemon = await response.json()
  console.log(pokemon)
  return pokemon
}
console.log(getPokemonData(25))

export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    NewMessage
  }
}
</script>
